  "description": "\"Do you know the story of Luminous?\"\n\nUplifting music and\nAn exciting work in which you defeat more and more monsters in the world of swords.\nAn impressive character advances through the ruins with the village's treasured sword\n\n□STORY\nThe boy's name is Luck.\nA villager living in a remote village.\nHe wants to be a hero.\nIt is said that anyone who sees Luminous will be praised by everyone.\nLuck took out the village sword to be praised by everyone.\n\n\"I want to be like a hero.\"\n\nLuck is determined in his heart,\nHe headed to the ruins where monsters were wandering.\nThe ruins of a monster that villagers do not approach.\nWill Luck be able to see the Luminous?\n\n□GAME\n・Easy control, simple sword attack and jump\n・Swing the sword down at the monster, cut vertically\n・Swing the sword from the side, cross\n・Attack quickly, thrust\n・Use three different attacks to defeat monsters\n・Explore by pressing a switch to open a closed door\n・Let's go see Luminous with Luck\n\n□SOUND\n・Rhythmic high-quality background music that beats the world of swords\n\n□SYSTEM\n・Every time you attack a monster, you get experience points.\n・Raise your level and defeat powerful enemies.\n",
